io.fsa.ver1
Class SubElementContainer

java.lang.Object
  io.fsa.ver1.SubElementContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Event, State, SubElement, Transition
public class SubElementContainer
extends Object
implements Cloneable

This class is the superclass of elements in an automaton. It provides operations for manipulating subelements of an element, e.g. observable, controllable. (Just make sure you type the names of the attributes in the same every time.)

Author:
Axel Gottlieb Michelsen, Kristian Edlund, Helen Bretzke
